<section class="panel reveal">
  <h1>About</h1>
  <p>Hi, I'm James and I'm passionate about all things geospatial. I completed my PhD in Data Analytics and Society at the University of Liverpool, focusing on building resilient coastal cities using remote sensing and big data analytics. Currently I'm working at the Barcelona Supercomputing Center as a Postdoctoral researcher/geospatial data scientist, where I co-ordinate the REALLOCATE Horizon project, and undertake my own independent research.</p>
  <p>I love working in Earth observation projects and have found my niche exploring the relationships between humans and the environment. I love collaboration, so feel free to reach out!</p>
</section>

